Subject: [PATCH] [Model] LongCat-2.0 support: config oe_* fields, identity
 experts, expert integration

- Add oe_vocab_size_ratio/oe_neighbor_num/oe_split_num to LongcatFlashConfig
- Remove @strict to allow extra config fields from LongCat-2.0
- Add @use_experts_implementation to LongcatFlashExperts
- Handle identity/zero experts in MoE forward pass
- Fix gate_up_proj shape (num_routed_experts, not total_experts)
- Ignore indexer weights on load

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
